(3, 'Canada Scholarship Opportunities for Bangladeshi Students 2022', 'Canada Scholarship Opportunities for Bangladeshi Students 2022', 'Canada has more than 500,000 international students and is ranked 3rd in international student attraction. Want to study in Canada from Bangladesh with a', 'Canada Scholarship Opportunities for Bangladeshi Students 2022', NULL, 0, '<p><strong>Why Canada is suitable for international students</strong></p><p>Canada has more than 500,000 international students and is ranked 3rd in international student attraction. Want to study in Canada from Bangladesh with a scholarship? There are various<a href=\"https://aeccglobal.com.bd/blog/scholarships-for-international-students-in-canada\"> scholarships in Canada for Bangladeshi students</a> that assist students financially. There are fully funded scholarships in Canada that help financially and provide other aid.</p><p>Canadian universities and colleges provide a wide range of scholarships to deserving international students to help them fund their studies. Many scholarships, grants, and bursaries are also offered by the Canadian government and public and private establishments.</p><p>There are different types of scholarships in Canada for&nbsp; international students:</p><ul><li><strong>Institutional Scholarships</strong></li></ul><p>They are scholarships in Canadian universities for international students usually funded by the institution. They offer undergraduate scholarships in Canada, like the University of Ontario Institute of Technology (UOIT) Undergraduate Research Award Canada, provided by the University of Ontario Institute of Technology.&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>Government Scholarships</strong></li></ul><p>The government of Canada funds them through awards, grants, or extending scholarships for international students in Canada.&nbsp;</p><ul><li><strong>Non- Governmental Scholarships</strong></li></ul><p>Various organizations, trusts, and foundations offer these scholarships to motivate students’ participation in the said field. They offer master’s scholarships in Canada like Pierre Elliott Trudeau Foundation Doctoral Fellowships– Canada.</p><p><strong>Scholarship options and monetary exemptions for bd students&nbsp;</strong></p><p>A scholarship is a financial aid awarded to a student to support his education expenses. There are a variety of scholarships available for students all over the world. Bangladeshi students can also avail these scholarships and pursue their education in some of the best universities in Canada. In this article, we will discuss getting a scholarship and how to apply for it.</p><p>If you are a Bangladeshi student and want to<a href=\"https://mystportal.com/canada/\"> study in Canada</a>, several scholarships are available. Getting a scholarship and applying for it can be daunting, but we will help you through it. In this article, we will discuss the different types of scholarships available and the process of applying for them. We will also talk about the requirements for each scholarship. So, read on and find out how you can study in Canada from Bangladesh with a scholarship.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h2><strong>Top 9 Scholarships in Canada for Bangladeshi Students</strong></h2><p><strong>The Government of Canada Scholarship Program:</strong> This program offers scholarships to students from countries with Canada having diplomatic relations.</p><p><strong>&nbsp;The Canadian Merit Scholarship Program: </strong>This program is offered by the government of Canada to students who have achieved high academic standing and demonstrated leadership qualities.</p><p><strong>The Canadian Commonwealth Scholarship Program:</strong> This program is offered to students from Commonwealth countries who want to study in Canada.</p><p><strong>The Quebec Scholarship Program: </strong>This program is offered by the government of Quebec to students who want to study in any field at any university in the province of Quebec.</p><p><strong>The Universi